# id: MappingRecordOperation -> public void setOutputRecordCreator(RecordCreator creator)
commentText:
Set a RecordCreator that should be used for creating default output Records._

Default is none: CCI's Interaction.execute variant_that returns an output Record will be called._

Specify a RecordCreator here if you always need to call CCI's_Interaction.execute variant with a passed-in output Record._This RecordCreator will then be invoked to create a default output Record instance._@see javax.resource.cci.Interaction#execute(javax.resource.cci.InteractionSpec, Record)_@see javax.resource.cci.Interaction#execute(javax.resource.cci.InteractionSpec, Record, Record)_@see org.springframework.jca.cci.core.CciTemplate#setOutputRecordCreator
codeText: public void setOutputRecordCreator(RecordCreator creator) {_		getCciTemplate().setOutputRecordCreator(creator)__	}
